0xC715F730.name: GET_VEHICLE_XENON_LIGHTS_CUSTOM_COLOR
0xC715F730.description: Returns vehicle xenon lights custom RGB color values. Do note this native doesn't return non-RGB colors that was set with [\_SET_VEHICLE_XENON_LIGHTS_COLOR](#\_0xE41033B25D003A07).
0xC715F730.resultsDescription: A boolean indicating if vehicle have custom xenon lights RGB color.
